<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 09:11:24 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>欧洲国家考虑在大流行关闭后重新开放驻朝鲜大使馆</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/european-countries-eye-reopening-embassies-north-korea-after-pandemic-closures-2024-02-28/</link><description>德国代表团自朝鲜大使馆在疫情期间关闭以来首次访问朝鲜首都平壤，而其他欧洲国家则在为预期的回归做准备。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 08:38:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/european-countries-eye-reopening-embassies-north-korea-after-pandemic-closures-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，Kedaara 即将为印度最大的私募基金筹集 17 亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/kedaara-close-raising-17-bln-indias-biggest-pe-fund-sources-say-2024-02-28/</link><description>两位直接了解情况的人士表示，Kedaara Capital 计划为印度有史以来最大的私募股权基金筹集 17 亿美元，这突显了印度经济从中国转移出去的情况下对该国快速增长的经济的巨大兴趣。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 06:51:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/kedaara-close-raising-17-bln-indias-biggest-pe-fund-sources-say-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾特使表示，特朗普担任总统期间印太立场没有变化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/no-change-indo-pacific-stance-under-trump-presidency-says-philippine-envoy-2024-02-28/</link><description>菲律宾长期驻华盛顿大使周三表示，如果唐纳德·特朗普在总统竞选中获胜，美国的印太战略不太可能改变。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 06:10:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/no-change-indo-pacific-stance-under-trump-presidency-says-philippine-envoy-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>由于对自由的担忧，香港准备制定更严格的安全法</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-moves-towards-enacting-tougher-security-law-amid-concerns-about-2024-02-28/</link><description>香港新国家安全法的公众咨询期于周三结束，人们担心当局希望尽快实施的这项立法将进一步侵蚀这个金融中心的自由。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 05:48:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-moves-towards-enacting-tougher-security-law-amid-concerns-about-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>需求预期看跌挑战铁矿石价格弹性</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/bearish-demand-expectations-challenge-iron-ores-price-resilience-2024-02-28/</link><description>尽管中国经济前景黯淡，但铁矿石价格长期保持坚挺，但自农历新年假期结束以来，铁矿石价格大幅下跌，引发了人们对需求疲软的担忧，并削弱了澳大利亚主要生产国的矿业股。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 05:12:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/bearish-demand-expectations-challenge-iron-ores-price-resilience-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>解说：碧桂园：债务问题有多严重？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/country-garden-how-bad-are-its-debt-problems-2024-02-28/</link><description>中国开发商碧桂园周三表示，因未支付 2.05 亿美元贷款而收到清算申请，这给其债务重组前景蒙上阴影，并削弱了北京方面恢复房地产行业信心的努力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 05:06:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/country-garden-how-bad-are-its-debt-problems-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>图瓦卢新政府重申与台湾的关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-tuvalu-government-reaffirms-relationship-with-taiwan-2024-02-28/</link><description>图瓦卢政府在一份声明中表示，图瓦卢新政府在上个月的选举后重申了与台湾的关系，并补充说它希望与澳大利亚就去年签署的安全协议进行对话。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 04:51:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-tuvalu-government-reaffirms-relationship-with-taiwan-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>香港取消房地产紧缩措施以协助经济复苏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-scraps-property-tightening-measures-aid-economic-recovery-2024-02-28/</link><description>香港周三宣布了重大措施，以提振疲软的房地产市场，取消所有住宅房地产紧缩措施，旨在帮助香港经济今年预计增长 2.5%-3.5%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 04:48:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-scraps-property-tightening-measures-aid-economic-recovery-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国西安将向新婚夫妇发放彩票以刺激生育</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-xian-give-lottery-tickets-newlyweds-bid-spur-births-2024-02-28/</link><description>中国西安市当局将斥资 70 万元人民币（合 97,000 美元）购买彩票，为出示结婚证的新婚夫妇颁发奖品，以鼓励在出生人口较少的时期举行婚礼。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 04:42:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-xian-give-lottery-tickets-newlyweds-bid-spur-births-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国鼎晖投资正在洽谈收购价值 17 亿美元的越南杂货连锁店的少数股权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-cdh-talks-buy-minority-stake-17-bln-vietnam-grocery-chain-say-sources-2024-02-28/</link><description>两名知情人士称，中国鼎晖投资公司正在就从越南零售商 Mobile World 手中收购 Bach Hoa Xanh (BHX) 少数股权进行深入谈判，这笔交易可能使这家杂货连锁店的估值高达 17 亿美元。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 04:41:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-cdh-talks-buy-minority-stake-17-bln-vietnam-grocery-chain-say-sources-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>丰田1月份全球产量增长7%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyotas-global-output-rises-by-7-january-2024-02-28/</link><description>日本丰田汽车周三表示，受益于美国强劲的需求，1 月份全球汽车产量增长 7%，连续第 13 个月同比增长。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 04:36:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyotas-global-output-rises-by-7-january-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，随着中海油退出，嘉能可关注壳牌新加坡资产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/glencore-eyes-shell-singapore-assets-cnooc-pulls-out-sources-say-2024-02-28/</link><description>几位行业和贸易消息人士称，瑞士矿业和大宗商品贸易商嘉能可(Glencore)正在考虑收购壳牌在新加坡的炼油厂和石化部门，该石油巨头在先前的收购者退出后正在寻找买家。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 04:27:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/glencore-eyes-shell-singapore-assets-cnooc-pulls-out-sources-say-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国扩大国家秘密法，将“工作秘密”纳入其中</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-broadens-law-state-secrets-include-work-secrets-2024-02-28/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，中国立法者自 2010 年以来首次扩大了北京的《国家秘密法》，根据网上发布的该法全文，将受限制的敏感信息范围扩大到“工作秘密”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 04:13:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-broadens-law-state-secrets-include-work-secrets-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>韩国和美国将举行年度演习，重点关注朝鲜核威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-us-stage-annual-drills-focusing-korea-nuclear-threats-2024-02-28/</link><description>官员周三表示，韩国和美国将于下周开始年度春季军事演习，重点是阻止朝鲜使用核武器的可能性。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 04:03:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-us-stage-annual-drills-focusing-korea-nuclear-threats-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国称其海警在台湾岛屿周围巡逻“无可非议”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-its-coast-guard-patrols-around-taiwan-islands-beyond-reproach-2024-02-28/</link><description>中国政府周三表示，中国海警在中国海岸附近的台湾岛屿周围的巡逻“无可非议”，并驳回了有关台湾游船登船引发恐慌的抱怨。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 03:21:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-its-coast-guard-patrols-around-taiwan-islands-beyond-reproach-2024-02-28/</guid></item></channel></rss>